ormal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信新城市602 office班人都o哂嘴，個場已經起左好幾日，無啦啦一日內拆哂佢即刻起碼冇左幾十萬，再加埋要同咁多商戶交代。到底有咩野神祕力量可以動搖佢地plan左咁耐既暑假展覽大計呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66165dc2d85aa00e4411a96149fc1533bee6af7d","tid":1317400,"uid":88785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"推到佢老母比車撞"},{"pid":"60b90b5de3151a4bc7f138e609ee26306c935676","tid":1317400,"uid":179144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"一班人衝入去lady M淨坐一日佢都幾奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec77ad87b5e9b6aaa438c2f1d2773a64f55271e","tid":1317400,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016d471692f2544cdee7f7c53b595799c0931437","tid":1317400,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"唔好推"},{"pid":"8e6d134d29e92e0522391e69d7ed35582859888d","tid":1317400,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4597b5ca11eabea626ff519931d216710135f8e","tid":1317400,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb444e0c6a22b5214ca75dbcaf496089b9fc196","tid":1317400,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002d2312cf5d7c6490e95e95fc6ad8f07ffd17a6","tid":1317400,"uid":78573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken